},
{
“type”: “dialogue”,
“character”: “Hetty”,
“text”: “Don’t seem too eager.”
},
{
“type”: “dialogue”,
“character”: “Harriet”,
“text”: “And yet if he charges only a thousand one might consider it.”
},
{
“type”: “dialogue”,
“character”: “Margaret”,
“text”: “If you really wish to be painted, why don’t you give a little more and have a portrait really worth while? John might be induced to do you for a little below his usual price considering that you used to be such good friends.”
},
{
“type”: “dialogue”,
“character”: “Hetty”,
“text”: “Hurrah!”
},
{
“type”: “dialogue”,
“character”: “Harriet”,
“text”: “That’s very nice of you to suggest – of course I don’t know –”
},
